This is a '''list of public art''' on permanent public display in [[Brisbane]], [[Queensland]], [[Australia]].
The list applies only to works of [[public art]] accessible in an outdoor public space; it does not include artwork on display inside museums. Public art may include [[sculpture]]s, [[statue]]s, [[monument]]s, memorials, [[mural]]s and [[mosaic]]s.
This list does not include military and war memorials.
